cat << EOF
This package offers a toolkit to render out a
datagrid in HTML format as well as
many other formats such as an XML Document, an
Excel Spreadsheet, an XUL Document and more.
It also offers paging and sorting
functionallity to limit the data that is
presented and processed.
This concept is based on the .NET Framework
DataGrid control and works very well with
database and XML result sets.
